Due to low cost, large-scale, layout flexibility, mobility support and other characteristics, industrial wireless sensor networking products in the mechanical parameters testing, industrial monitoring, smart power, mining safety, health, environmental monitoring and other industry applications has been widely attention. At the same time, industrial wireless sensor networking products also face prolonged nodes working hours, increase the communication distance, miniaturization, standardization and other technical challenges and finding scenarios and other market challenges.
In 2014, domestic scale sensor applications in the industrial sector reached 14.31 billion yuan, and wireless sensor network products accounted for in the industrial sensor market is only 4.3%, the size of about 6.2 billion. By 2019, the domestic industrial wireless sensor networking products accounted for in the industrial sensor market will be more than 10.0%, the scale is expected to reach 2.42 billion yuan, the annual compound growth rate of 27.1%, the market prospect is broad.";s:8:"keywords";s:42:"工业，无线传感器，网络，产品";s:11:"description";s:42:"工业，无线传感器，网络，产品";s:8:"contents";s:358:"2014年，国内传感器在工业领域的应用规模达到143.1亿元，而无线传感器网络产品在工业传感器市场中的占比仅4.3%，规模约6.2亿元。到2019年，国内工业无线传感器网络产品在工业传感器市场中的占比将超过10.0%，规模预计达24.2亿元，年复合增长率高达27.1%，市场前景广阔。";s:5:"photo";s:17:"5720b37c829c1.jpg";s:3:"pid";s:2:"12";s:3:"bid";s:1:"2";s:4:"sort";s:1:"5";s:4:"time";s:10:"1460599757";}i:5;a:15:{s:2:"id";s:2:"10";s:5:"title";s:42:"高精密电流测量仪研究项目启动";s:3:"url";s:14:"High-precision";s:6:"etitle";s:70:"High-precision current measurement instrument research project started";s:9:"ekeywords";s:70:"High-precision current measurement instrument research project started";s:12:"edescription";s:70:"High-precision current measurement instrument research project started";s:9:"econtents";s:1455:"Instrumentation News: January 6, major scientific instruments developed by the national special wide amount AQSIQ organizations limit high precision current measurement instrument project start will be held at the China Institute of Metrology. Research indicates that China's current traceability system that accurately measured the magnitude of the official launch.<br />
Electricity metering metering modern science the most widely used measurement and the current measurement is the core and foundation of electrical measurement. Domestic and foreign common method of measuring the current using Ohm's law, measuring the voltage drop across the resistor current to be measured on the produce to achieve, this method of measurement is facing one of the biggest problems that the current through the resistor will heat up when the device caused by the resistance value changes, resulting in a measurement error. Therefore, to reduce the load coefficient of resistance (the resistance value of the current through the resistance of the device under test due to heat caused by relative changes, known as "load factor") has become the key to the current precision measurement. At present, how to reduce the various types of current measuring instrument sampling resistor load factor, and accurate calibration of various sampling resistor load factor actually used it has become a major bottleneck world precision current measurement technology development.";s:8:"keywords";s:24:"高精密电流测量仪";s:11:"description";s:24:"高精密电流测量仪";s:8:"contents";s:1066:"仪器仪表网讯：1月6日，由国家质检总局组织的国家重大科学仪器设备开发专项宽量限超高精密电流测量仪项目启动会在中国计量科学研究院召开。这标志着我国电流准确量值计量溯源体系研究正式启动。
	电学计量是现代计量科学中应用最为广泛的计量，而电流测量是电学计量的核心和基础。国内外测量电流的普遍方法是利用欧姆定律，测量待测电流在电 阻上产生的电压降来实现，这种测量方法面临着一个最大的困扰，那就是电流通过电阻器件时会发热而导致电阻值发生变化，从而产生测量误差。因此，减小电阻的 负载系数(电流通过待测电阻器件时因发热而引起的电阻值相对变化，称“负载系数”)成为电流精密测量的关键所在。目前，如何降低各种类型的电流测量仪中采 样电阻的负载系数，并准确校验各种实际使用的采样电阻负载系数已成为世界各国精密电流测量技术发展的重大瓶颈问题。";s:5:"photo";s:17:"5720b386d31f1.jpg";s:3:"pid";s:2:"12";s:3:"bid";s:1:"2";s:4:"sort";s:1:"6";s:4:"time";s:10:"1460600132";}}}
